{"id":19899,"date":"2014-09-29T11:17:51","date_gmt":"2014-09-29T07:17:51","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=19899"},"modified":"2023-04-21T15:51:49","modified_gmt":"2023-04-21T11:51:49","slug":"enjoin-follow-sahabah","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/09\/29\/enjoin-follow-sahabah\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Sahaba: I enjoin you to follow my companions"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, &#8220;<strong>I enjoin you to follow my companions, then those after them and those after them. Thereafter, falsehood will spread until a man offers his oath without being asked and a witness gives testimony without being asked. No doubt, a man is not in seclusion with a woman but that Satan is the third of them. Hold fast to the community and beware of division, for Satan is with one alone and he is further from two together. Whoever wants the best place in Paradise, let him hold fast to the community. Whoever rejoices with his good deeds and is saddened by his evil deeds is the believer among you<\/strong>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2165<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0637\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0623\u064f\u0648\u0635\u0650\u064a\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0623\u064e\u0635\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u064a \u062b\u064f\u0645\u0651\u064